Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year After Colony 175...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...the leader of the colonies\Nwas assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Gundams were sent\Nto Earth to take revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since OZ's activities\Nin space...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...took the form of cooperation\Nrather than control...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...the colonies decided\Nto accept OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The year After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As OZ moves to take over\Nboth Earth and outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gundams are labeled rebels\Nand are isolated from society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With no place to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gundams and\Ntheir pilots...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...must fight for a reason to\Nexist in the changing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's for the peace\Nof the colony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fighting for the peace\Nof the colony as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're both fighting for{\i0}\N{\i1}the colonies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are we enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're 90% finished attaching\Nthe satellite drive mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would mean a total\Nof about ten days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...to move to OZ's power zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact Colonel Une so I can\Ngive her a progress report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An unidentified shuttle\Nis headed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's quite small\Nfor a shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Its lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried contacting them,\Nbut they still won't respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get hold of security and have\Nthem guard our defense line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is OZ Unit 171.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Approaching shuttle,{\i0}\N{\i1}consider this a warning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Change your course at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you come any closer,{\i0}\N{\i1}we'll open fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is not a bluff,{\i0}\N{\i1}it's a warning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The flying object has\Nbeen destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission com...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mobile suit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transforming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy mobile suit hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's off balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's really a Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it wouldn't fall\Nthis easily!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm too lenient am I,\NChief Engineer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it's too risky\Nto depend on those pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those associated with\Nthe Gundams...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...are still valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot of Zero One has already\Nmastered the Mercurius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no OZ pilot\Nhas skills exceeding his.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With the colonies arming\Nthemselves, they're isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't make any\Ncareless moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparations to mass-produce\Nthe Vayeate and Mercurius...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the Lunar Base is\Nunder way, as arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not needed any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tubarov, why do you\Ndislike them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something to\Nbe proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Colonel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've received an{\i0}\N{\i1}urgent message!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A natural resource satellite at{\i0}\N{\i1}point 07 U 1 has disappeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What, an enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, a new Gundam that{\i0}\N{\i1}we have no data on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The satellite and the troops{\i0}\N{\i1}and units on it have vanished!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know\Na Gundam did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We heard from someone{\i0}\N{\i1}we think is the enemy pilot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he'd destroy the{\i0}\N{\i1}civilian colony at point 06E.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He sent us this secret{\i0}\N{\i1}blueprint.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Probably that of Gundam Zero Four!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a declaration of war?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the Vayeate and\NMercurius to Colony 06E.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's send out the\NTaurus mobile dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep using them\Nto guard the Lunar Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out the Vayeate\Nand Mercurius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The firepower of both\Nthe Vayeate and Mercurius...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...surpasses that of the Tauruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Send out the orders.\N- Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The young men responsible\Nfor changing the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sure panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,An unidentified Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...has declared its plans\Nto destroy a colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidentified?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What about its specs\Nand weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any\Ndetailed information?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They know it's associated...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the Gundam Zero Four, Sandrock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Quatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...it has the power to wipe out\Na natural resource satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go confirm what they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprint you left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the size of the\Nresource satellite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...but such destructive power\Npoints to that blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Five of us designed the\Noriginal Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has completed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense something dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a layman knows that\Nmuch power's unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that the\Npilot's using it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...proves he's either ignorant\Nor reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he's doing something\Neven we hesitated to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of colonies are\Ngonna disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, No. 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a better pilot than\NNo. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in on the next battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in your shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a Gundam pilot might\Nget himself killed this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're up against\Na Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it's a new model.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He wiped out a whole OZ\Ndivision with just one suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are its specs and\Nweapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're a secret agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The engineers asked the\Nsame questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With the red one, the Mercurius,\Nthis should be quite a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming; like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll just stand\Nback and watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...as two Gundam pilots fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a suit\Nperformance test!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't help them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get your turn eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was no act.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to worry\Nabout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a traitor wouldn't\Nbring us a gift like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Duo Maxwell and{\i0}\N{\i1}Wu Fei Chang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master O gave me this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use it to kill time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The carrier for the\NVayeate and Mercurius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Duo and Wu Fei's\NGundams have been upgraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the pilot of the\Nnew Gundam is Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The time may have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we join up with Quatre,\Nwe'll attack OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know\Nhe's our ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Assumptions lead to mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we're piloting\NOZ's mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be forced to\Nbattle with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's a strong ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...we might have the force\Nneeded to fight OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if his Gundam is\Nlacking in power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll end up destroying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be more advantageous{\i0}\N{\i1}for you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to keep hiding within OZ{\i0}\N{\i1}until you can defeat Treize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we'll know\Nafter this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've evacuated the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy could show up\Nanywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Be on the lookout!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Section 1: Everything's{\i0}\N{\i1}under control!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Section 2: Under control!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside of the colony is\Nequipped with beam cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The colony can defend itself\Nno matter what enemies approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling Colony 06E3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to eliminate\Nyour colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No sense retaliating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the colony at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the colony at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire the outer\Nbeam cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of dying,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you shouldn't be\Nfighting in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have tears in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're awake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was quick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our destination just changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were too late to{\i0}\N{\i1}save that colony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he'd be destroying{\i0}\N{\i1}a colony in this area next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This carrier sticks out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll proceed in the{\i0}\N{\i1}mobile suits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our objective is to find out{\i0}\N{\i1}how powerful the Gundam is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll fight only if necessary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Quatre we're up against.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we don't need to worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa, be cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, he just destroyed\Na colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll lure the enemy in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mercurius, move in alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attack the enemy on sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Officer Trowa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aren't you giving that former{\i0}\N{\i1}Gundam pilot too much freedom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the switch to his\Nself-detonation device.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's completely focused\Non the Gundam right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees it as an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it'll be completed\Nin one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Quatre is back,\Nwe're going to be busy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't consider an\Nunconfirmed Gundam an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Gundam is defeating\NOZ's troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where the air supply\Nfor the cells is controlled?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's controlled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tubarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cutting off the air\Nsupply to the prisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't received such orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these orders from\NColonel Une?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving out these orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just doing\Nas ordered, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That Lady Une's a little\Ntoo soft for her own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My knees are feeling weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, they've cut off\Nour air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks, you already noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my efforts were wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you old men\Nworrying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got thirty minutes\Nat the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret that we\Ncouldn't complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...our upgrade of the\NDeathscythe and Shenlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna die then\Nhurry up and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know they hate\Npersistent old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've gotta be persistent\Nto get anything out of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dinky way\Nto kill us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've gone\Nto battle, instead of Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Wu Fei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no sense studying\Nthat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm if you want\Nto live a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of luck unless\Nsomething drastic happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing everything I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...in case "something drastic"\Ndoes happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wu Fei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm gonna\Nthrow in the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is such a lame\Nway to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so "not cool"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The motion sensor detects\Nnothing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you really think he's here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Couldn't he have already{\i0}\N{\i1}gone to a different area?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Gundam's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The colony doesn't need\Nthings like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the colony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the colony really\Nneeds is a war!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three suits in the{\i0}\N{\i1}colony are down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gundam's coming out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Quatre, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what that\NGundam can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the new Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, there's no worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This Gundam is unparalleled!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quatre, this is Trowa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you read me, Quatre?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I read you, Trowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer, Trowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get any closer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trowa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Outer space has gone mad{\i0}\N{\i1}so I'll destroy it all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I must destroy all the weapons\Nthat have accumulated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies are becoming\Narmed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the colonies\Nmust also be destroyed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Quatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the others for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm telling you not{\i0}\N{\i1}to get any closer!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got\Nto say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything has gone mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I'll just fight,\Nbelieving in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quatre, I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile doll project\Nis another step toward...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Romefeller Foundation's\Nconquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize opposes this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...and steps down from\Nhis position as OZ leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam pilots cause\Na blood bath in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...as they continue their\Nmortal battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,During the battle, Trowa\Nis thrown out of his suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...and drifts into the\Nsilent depths of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 25,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:23:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Quatre vs. Heero".
